            <lb />The <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon</name>, which<lb />
            <seg ana="#exact_reproduction" resp="#np" type="topic">
                reproduces absolutely the
                <lb />Artists' original renderings
            </seg>,
            <lb />retains its position amongst
            <lb />the World's foremost and
            <lb />greatest reproducing instru-
            <lb />ments.
            <lb />The <name type="brand">Steinway
            Welte</name> is
            <lb />made also as a self-contained
            <lb />upright piano. Welte cabi-
            <lb />nets when desired can be
            <lb />supplied separately for at-
            <lb />tachment to any pianoforte.
